overview.en: The total amount of OLY issued is 600 million, and will never be issued. OLY is a decentralized blockchain digital asset based on the encrypted digital algorithm programming platform Ethereum (Ethereum). It is a standard token based on the Ethereum blockchain. OLY is the Olympic star AY coin, which is used to intelligently produce the coin OLY through its own AY computing power value.
overview.zh: OLY 发行总量为 6 亿枚，永不增发。OLY 是基于加密数字算 法编程平台以太坊（Ethereum）发行的去中心化的区块链数字资产， 它是基于以太坊区块链的标准代币。OLY 为奥运之星 AY 子币，用 来通过自身 AY 算力值智能产出子币 OLY。
